  "title": "Pet Groomer (Gross approx. S$2,600 to S$4,000)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Descriptions:</strong></p><p>As a Pet Groomer, you will help manage the day-to-day business operations of the Pet Grooming Centre.</p><p>Being part of the retail team, you help to build and develop a dynamic team who understands the business objectives and the importance of having the ability to deliver a Pet Lovers Centre customer service & shopping experience that is a cut above the rest.</p><p>Your roles & responsibilities include:</p><p>• Manage the day-to-day business operations of grooming centre within the retail store;</p><p>• Ensure all grooming appointments properly scheduled;</p><p>• Ensure pet grooming equipment are well maintained;</p><p>• Perform pet grooming based on the best practices and customers’ needs;</p><p>• Ensure workplace safety, hygiene level and cleanliness of the grooming centre;</p><p>• Ensure safety of pets throughout the grooming process;</p><p>• Ensure that all pets are well taken care of and in compliance with AVA guidelines;</p><p>• Highlight abnormalities of pets to the customers to avoid unnecessary conflicts or misunderstanding.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least 2 to 3 years of experience in cutting & shaving furs for dogs/cats/rabbits.</p></li><li><p>Possess relevant grooming certificate.<br /></p></li></ul><p>Interested Applicant, Please Whatsapp to 98272969 or login to https://plc.applyourjobs.com/ to apply.</p><p>6 days work week, including weekends and public holidays</p><p>Incentives Ranging from S$360 to S$1,300</p><p>Annual Variable Bonus</p><p>Benefits: Medical Reimbursement, Health Insurance, Quarterly Meal Allowance, Team Bonding, Long Service Award, Medical Reimbursement, Health Insurance, Staff Purchase Discount, Company Uniform Provided, etc.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
